set relativenumber

" Vim remaps
noremap <a-j> gt
noremap <a-k> gT
inoremap jj <Esc>
noremap <space>y "*y
noremap <space>Y "*Y
noremap <space>p "*p
noremap <space>P "*P

" IntelliJ remaps
nnoremap g] :action GotoImplementation<cr>
nnoremap g[ :action GotoSuperMethod<cr>

nnoremap <space>u :action FindUsages<cr>
nnoremap <space>T :action GotoSymbol<cr>
nnoremap <space>a :action GotoAction<cr>
nnoremap <space>rr :action RenameElement<cr>

nnoremap \r :action RunClass<cr>
nnoremap \R :action Run<cr>
nnoremap \d :action DebugClass<cr>
nnoremap \D :action Debug<cr>
nnoremap \c :action CheckStyleCurrentFileAction<cr>

" In IDE changes
" <C-k> to Up
" <C-j> to Down
" <a-o> to Quick Doc
" <a-i> to Error Description

" Change java tabs to 2, similar to Google
" Plugins: checkstyle, python, take down unused plugins.
